_sText:
A Port of my CSGO Map, de_dome to Counter-Strike Source

Original Description:
==NOT MEANT FOR COMPETITIVE PLAY==

Welcome to de_dome, A Casual 10v10 Map That Was Made By Miguelsgamingch

Backstory:
The SEAL Team 6 Mission is simple, take over the Terrorists base, they landed at the helipad but terrorists were alerted, leading to chaos, meanwhile the terrorist has to abort from defending the base, they were contacted to instead blow to the base up, and here we are.

Made In 3 & A Half Days

=Errors=
-Bots work 60% Fine, they always hide in crates and usually gets stuck on this wooden plank which is secretly a door, there's a handle kind of thing next to it however bots don't use the handle.
-Shadows on the helicopter is dark, really dark, you can comment if you want it to be gone.
-For some reason it only spawns 4 bots (+1 = you) which means its a 5v5... not a 10v10, you can add bots via devconsole if you want 10v10.
-Other than that nothing much else
